<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  Static — covers the stable public routes only. Product pages (/shop/:id)
  are intentionally excluded: they're per-product and change as stock/catalog
  changes, which needs server-side generation from the product list to stay
  accurate. They're still crawlable via internal links from /shop. A future
  improvement would be a backend-generated sitemap (e.g. GET /sitemap.xml
  querying active products) if organic product-page search traffic becomes
  a priority.

  Excluded on purpose (matches robots.txt Disallow list): /cart, /checkout,
  /dashboard and other authenticated/personal/transactional routes.
-->
